Quote:  The Golden Bauble Award. Winston Peters wins this one from United Future leader Peter Dunne by a country mile, not only because he was cynical enough to grab the baubles of ministerial office with both hands even after telling his supporters he had no interest in the said perks, but because of his brashness in claiming it was all a media beat-up.
